{"tid":2190563,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中印衝突】印媒：兩國邊境部署逾百坦克 「已進入對方射程內」","createTime":"2020-09-05T18:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T02:35:19.000Z","uid":261647,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b298783a696f725329a0d24b431e35430cb87785","tid":2190563,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U1CvJBV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU1CvJBV.png&h=eabb9685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度T90S坦克（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n中印邊境持續緊張。印度傳媒《今日印度》（India Today）前日報道，印度陸軍已經在斯潘古爾湖和楚舒勒之間的平原上部署一個坦克團（約108輛坦克），該處正是今年８月，中印士兵發生衝突附近位置。除了印軍，解放軍亦在附近佈署坦克和裝甲車。<br />\n●印度部署逾百輛坦克<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，印度和中國的坦克已經部署到距離很近的地方，進入彼此的射程內，雙方目前仍在進行對話。解放軍的坦克和裝甲車輛部署在靠近Kala Top附近的丘陵地區，Kala Top目前由印軍所佔據。<br />\n<br />\n印度軍方說，解放軍的重型坦克和輕型坦克部署位置處在印度駐軍的火力範圍以內。印度駐軍全副武裝，擁有坦克和火砲的支援。《今日印度》表示，由於Kala Top附近的印軍佔據制高點，擁有地利，因此解放軍坦克和機械化步兵並未再推進。報道又稱，為了緩解局勢，雙方的軍事會談在摩爾多附近進行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200903/4UYMB6RCCBA3TCIDCRUWUFC5XU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200903%2F4UYMB6RCCBA3TCIDCRUWUFC5XU%2F&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=3f20aebb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200903%2F4UYMB6RCCBA3TCIDCRUWUFC5XU%2F&h=263ea38d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200903/4UYMB6RCCBA3TCIDCRUWUFC5XU/</a>"},{"pid":"40cd01812bcfd758bf03bcdb2890bc56246e5e51","tid":2190563,"uid":156652,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cuFmpi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cuFmpi.gif&h=c1e830a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d05c29ad49451ee080fed8ba8c8b69b5cc0297d","tid":2190563,"uid":10788,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:44:41.000Z","msg":"印度加油 炸佢老母"}